*************************************************
  REXSETUP - A distutils extension package for RexRunner applications
*************************************************


Distutils extensions
====================

RR defines a Distutils extensions for distributing static files
together with Python packages.  To use, for every project with
static files, add the following lines to ``setup.py``::

    setup(
        ...
        setup_requires=['rexsetup'],
        www_dir='...',
        www_prefix='...',
        www_module='...',
        www_settings='...',
        ...
    )

`www_dir`
    A relative path to the directory with static files;
`www_prefix`
    The default URL root; if not set, use ``/project_name``.
`www_module`
    Python module or package which registers plugins and extensions.
`www_settings`
    A file containing default configuration parameters.


